00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,910
Which is supposed to be better luck, sue-kichi or kichi?

365
00:18:05,910 --> 00:18:07,380
I think it's sue-kichi.

366
00:18:09,650 --> 00:18:12,150
From the top, dai-kichi, chu-kichi, shou-kichi, kichi,

367
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:14,550
han-kichi, sue-kichi, sue-shou-kichi.

368
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:16,990
So kichi is better.

369
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:18,120
Th-Thanks.

370
00:18:18,530 --> 00:18:20,030
I see.

371
00:18:20,030 --> 00:18:23,560
Now I feel like getting a fortune, too.

372
00:18:25,630 --> 00:18:26,930
Ah, whoops.

