Kumiko Oumae

391
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:08,840
Are you eating?

392
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:09,840
No.

393
00:20:09,840 --> 00:20:10,830
Tap

394
00:20:31,060 --> 00:20:32,550
It isn't working...

395
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:33,730
Huh?

396
00:20:33,730 --> 00:20:34,960
Where did you get that?

397
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,800
I bought it.

398
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:39,130
Bought it? You actually bought it?

399
00:20:39,130 --> 00:20:40,860
Yeah, just this.

400
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:42,800
It's too early.

401
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:45,010
You haven't even chosen an instrument...

402
00:20:45,010 --> 00:20:45,730
Huh?

403
00:20:46,770 --> 00:20:48,610
How do you play it?

404
00:20:48,610 --> 00:20:50,680
I used to play contrabass.

405
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:52,080
Teach me.

406
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:54,770
Um...

407
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:57,940
Your lips.

408
00:20:58,420 --> 00:21:01,150
Make your lips vibrate, like this.

409
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:03,780
Try it.

410
00:21:06,290 --> 00:21:08,760
Now try it with the mouthpiece.

411
00:21:12,100 --> 00:21:13,230
Not bad.

412
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:18,340
It worked!

413
00:21:18,340 --> 00:21:19,970
It worked, right?

414
00:21:19,970 --> 00:21:21,010
Yeah.

415
00:21:21,010 --> 00:21:23,140
It worked! I made a sound!

416
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:24,980
How did you do it?

417
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:26,110
I don't know!

418
00:21:27,950 --> 00:21:29,920
Oh, Kumiko-chan...

419
00:21:30,850 --> 00:21:33,580
Do you want to join the concert band with us?

420
00:21:43,830 --> 00:21:44,590
Okay.

421
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,130
Really?

422
00:21:46,470 --> 00:21:47,370
Yeah.

423
00:21:47,370 --> 00:21:48,770
Yay.

424
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:54,230
And so, I joined the Kitauji
High School Concert Band.

425
